quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  55,73,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  55,74,"Ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú kan kò fọwọ́ kàn wọ́n rí ṣíwájú wọn."
  55,75,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  56,64,"ṣé ẹ̀yin l’ẹ̀ ń jẹ́ kí ó hù jáde tàbí Àwa l’À ń jẹ́ kí ó hù jáde?"
  56,65,"Tí A bá fẹ́ ni, Àwa ìbá sọ ọ́ di gbígbẹ, ẹ̀yin yó sì máa ṣèèmọ̀ (tí ẹ óò máa ká àbámọ̀)."
  56,66,"(Ẹ̀yin yó sì wí pé:) “Dájúdájú àwa ti di onígbèsè.”"
  64,16,"Nítorí náà, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu bí ẹ bá ṣe lágbára mọ. Ẹ gbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ (Allāhu), ẹ tẹ̀lé e, kí ẹ sì náwó (fún ẹ̀sìn Rẹ̀) lóore jùlọ fún ẹ̀mí yín. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí A bá ṣọ́ níbi ahun àti ọ̀kánjúà inú ẹ̀mí rẹ̀, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn gan-an ni olùjèrè."
  64,17,"Tí ẹ bá yá Allāhu ní dúkìá tó dára, Ó máa ṣàdìpèlé rẹ̀ fún yín. Ó sì máa foríjìn yín. Allāhu sì ni Ọlọ́pẹ́{1}, Aláfaradà,.",1:[Nínú orúkọ àti ìròyìn Allāhu ni “Ṣākir” àti “Ṣakūr”.]
  64,18,"Onímọ̀-ìkọ̀kọ̀ àti gban̄gba, Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n."
  66,7,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ ṣàì gbàgbọ́, ẹ má ṣe ṣàròyé ní ọjọ́ òní. Ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́ ni A óò fi san yín ní ẹ̀san."
  66,8,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, ẹ ronú pìwàdà sí ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu ní ìronúpìwàdà òdodo. Ó ṣeé ṣe pé Olúwa yín máa pa àwọn àṣìṣe yín rẹ́ fún yín. Ó sì máa mu yín wọ inú àwọn Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra tí àwọn odò ń ṣàn ní ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀. Ní ọjọ́ tí Allāhu kò níí dójú ti Ànábì àti àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo pẹ̀lú rẹ̀. Ìmọ́lẹ̀ wọn yóò máa tàn ní iwájú wọn àti ní ọwọ́ ọ̀tún wọn. Wọn yóò sọ pé: “Olúwa wa, pé ìmọ́lẹ̀ wa fún wa, kí O sì foríjìn wá. Dájúdájú Ìwọ ni Alágbára lórí gbogbo n̄ǹkan.”"
  66,9,"Ìwọ Ànábì, gbógun ti àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ àti àwọn ṣọ̀bẹ-ṣèlu mùsùlùmí. Kí o sì le mọ́ wọn. Ibùgbé wọn sì ni iná Jahanamọ. Ìkángun náà sì burú."
  67,4,"Lẹ́yìn náà, wò ó padà ní ẹ̀ẹ̀ mejì, kí ojú rẹ padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ pẹ̀lú ìyẹpẹrẹ. Ó sì máa káàárẹ̀."
  67,5,"Dájúdájú A ti fi (àwọn ìràwọ̀ tó ń tànmọ́lẹ̀ bí) àtùpà ṣe sánmọ̀ ilé ayé ní ọ̀ṣọ́. A tún ṣe wọ́n ni ẹ̀ta-ìràwọ̀ tí wọ́n ń jù mọ́ àwọn aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n. A sì pèsè ìyà Iná tó ń jó sílẹ̀ dè wọ́n."
  67,6,"Ìyà iná Jahanamọ sì wà fún àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́. Ìkángun náà sì burú."